{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回　星殒月落：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第十二回星殒月落熊倜心理上纷乱的情形，正如一团乱麻。熊倜草草与飞鹤子等道别过，独自驰下山去，最使他惊异的山下竟不时遇见黑衣劲装的汉子，分明都是天阴教的爪牙。使熊倜深深地吸了口气，觉出武当山实是处于极不利的地位。熊倜惴惴不安的回至谷城客栈。夜色沉沉地垂下了一层黑影，熊倜的心快要燃烧起来，本想连夜赶往江陵，而怪异的事又发生了。熊倜要些菜饭狼章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是你家的朋友，你家还不晓得吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夏姊姊天天巴望您，若不是她……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她怎么了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是有人难为她，熊某可不能善罢甘休！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "芸姊姊首先和叶清清交成好友，又得九天仙子爱顾，谁敢来难为她，又是你熊大侠的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快请进来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让我这几个小妹妹，各敬两位一杯，然后就送熊小弟弟和夏妹妹……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虬须客，什么，他在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夏姑娘只身放浪江湖，虬须客自然不会放心她的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倜哥，你怎不早些来看我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还是嘴上不饶人，诚心挖苦我是不是？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算了！难道大家不称你是武林三秀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是柳姑娘指示，我就去通知熊大哥一声，至于天阴教……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尚当家的还没决定主意么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 699,
      "line_end": 699
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尚大哥半夜来找我，有要事么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 749,
      "line_end": 749
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么三位请吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 819,
      "line_end": 819
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎不见我们的马匹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 825,
      "line_end": 825
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送客送客送客，为什么敲锣呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 837,
      "line_end": 837
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 839,
      "line_end": 839
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "落地流星",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 951,
      "line_end": 951
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再会",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1105,
      "line_end": 1105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "需要什么珍贵的药？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1129,
      "line_end": 1129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1135,
      "line_end": 1135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你最好把她送回落日马场休养。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1137,
      "line_end": 1137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尚大哥怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1139,
      "line_end": 1139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去打探一下，看他被关在哪里，再设法救他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1141,
      "line_end": 1141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1143,
      "line_end": 1143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun_ucazn_ubjzm_di",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸诧异地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道我爹姓萨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1183,
      "line_end": 1183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun_ubkra",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸惊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1191,
      "line_end": 1191
    }
  ],
